---
const title = "Bicicleta Ergométrica: Guia de Compra e Comparativos";
const description = "Comparamos especificações, analisamos avaliações reais e explicamos a ficha técnica em linguagem simples. Encontre a ergométrica certa para o seu perfil.";
const siteUrl = "https://bicicletasergometricas.com";
const canonicalUrl = siteUrl + "/";

const schemaOrg = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebSite",
  name: "Bicicletas Ergométricas",
  url: siteUrl,
  description,
};
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonicalUrl} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />

    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:url" content={canonicalUrl} />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Bicicletas Ergométricas" />

    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={title} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={description} />

    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;1,9..40,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css" />

    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schemaOrg)} />
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900 antialiased">

    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-gray-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-4 py-3">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-emerald-700 text-lg" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="18.5" cy="17.5" r="3.5"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="17.5" r="3.5"/><circle cx="15" cy="5" r="1"/><path d="M12 17.5V14l-3-3 4-3 2 3h2"/>
          </svg>
          Bicicletas Ergométricas
        </a>
        <nav aria-label="Navegação principal" class="hidden gap-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 md:flex">
          <a href="/guia" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Guia de Compra</a>
          <a href="/comparativos/mecanica-vs-magnetica" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Comparativos</a>
          <a href="/como-usar" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Como Usar</a>
          <a href="/sobre" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Sobre</a>
        </nav>
        <a href="/ferramentas/quiz-qual-ergometrica" class="hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg bg-rose-500 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-rose-600 transition-colors">
          Qual é a minha? →
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="main-content">

      <!-- HERO -->
      <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-rose-500 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Curadoria independente</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl leading-tight mb-5 text-gray-900" style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700;">
            Encontre a bicicleta ergométrica certa para você
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 mb-8">
            Comparamos especificações, analisamos avaliações reais de compradores e explicamos a ficha técnica em linguagem simples. Sem achismos, sem enrolação.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <a href="/ferramentas/quiz-qual-ergometrica" class="bg-rose-500 hover:bg-rose-600 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors text-center">
              Descobrir qual é a minha →
            </a>
            <a href="/guia" class="border border-gray-300 hover:border-gray-400 text-gray-700 font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors text-center">
              Ver guia de compra
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- PERFIS -->
      <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Qual é o seu perfil?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Cada perfil tem necessidades diferentes. Veja a recomendação certa para você.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <a href="/reviews/ergometrica-silenciosa-apartamento" class="group border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 group-hover:bg-rose-200 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Moro em apartamento</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Silêncio é prioridade. Veja os modelos magnéticos que não incomodam os vizinhos.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/reviews/ergometrica-para-idosos" class="group border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 group-hover:bg-rose-200 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Para idosos ou reabilitação</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Baixo impacto articular, acesso fácil e encosto lombar. Modelos horizontais indicados.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/reviews/ergometrica-acima-100kg" class="group border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 group-hover:bg-rose-200 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Acima de 100 kg</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Estrutura reforçada e carga máxima real. Saiba o que verificar antes de comprar.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/reviews/ergometrica-reabilitacao" class="group border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 group-hover:bg-rose-200 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Pós-operatório / fisioterapia</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Modelos indicados para reabilitação de joelho, quadril e coluna.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/comparativos/ergometrica-vs-spinning" class="group border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 group-hover:bg-rose-200 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Quero treinar de verdade</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Alta intensidade, HIIT e performance. Compare ergométrica com spinning.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/ferramentas/quiz-qual-ergometrica" class="group border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 group-hover:bg-rose-200 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Ainda não sei qual quero</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Responda 5 perguntas e descubra o modelo ideal para o seu caso.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- COMPARATIVOS -->
      <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Comparativos populares</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">As dúvidas mais comuns antes de comprar, respondidas com dados reais.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="/comparativos/mecanica-vs-magnetica" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-start transition-all hover:shadow-sm group">
              <div class="flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 group-hover:bg-rose-100 group-hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 2v2m0 16v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41m11.32 11.32l1.41 1.41M2 12h2m16 0h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Mecânica vs Magnética</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Qual a diferença real no dia a dia? Ruído, manutenção e custo-benefício comparados.</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/comparativos/ergometrica-vs-spinning" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-start transition-all hover:shadow-sm group">
              <div class="flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 group-hover:bg-rose-100 group-hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Ergométrica vs Spinning</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Para qual objetivo cada uma serve melhor? Descubra antes de gastar errado.</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/comparativos/ergometrica-vs-esteira" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-start transition-all hover:shadow-sm group">
              <div class="flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 group-hover:bg-rose-100 group-hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Ergométrica vs Esteira</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Gasto calórico, impacto articular e espaço: qual vale mais para o seu caso.</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/comparativos/ergometrica-vs-eliptico" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-rose-300 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-start transition-all hover:shadow-sm group">
              <div class="flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 group-hover:bg-rose-100 group-hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors">Ergométrica vs Elíptico</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Dois cardios de baixo impacto: qual escolher para o seu objetivo e espaço.</p>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- COMO AVALIAMOS -->
      <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Como fazemos nossas recomendações</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-10">Nossas análises são baseadas em especificações técnicas dos fabricantes, avaliações verificadas de compradores e histórico de reclamações. Sem patrocínio de marcas.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="mx-auto mb-3 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Avaliações reais</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Centenas de avaliações verificadas de compradores na Amazon, Shopee e Mercado Livre.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="mx-auto mb-3 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Reclame Aqui</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Mapeamos reclamações por modelo e marca. Você sabe os problemas reais antes de comprar.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="mx-auto mb-3 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Fichas técnicas</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Traduzimos jargão técnico para linguagem simples. Você entende o que está comprando.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/sobre" class="mt-8 inline-block text-sm text-emerald-700 underline hover:text-emerald-800">
            Saiba mais sobre nossa metodologia →
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 py-8 text-sm text-gray-500">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 text-center">
        <p class="mb-2">
          <strong class="text-gray-700" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Bicicletas Ergométricas</strong> — Curadoria independente para quem quer pedalar em casa com segurança.
        </p>
        <nav aria-label="Links do rodapé" class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/sobre" class="hover:text-emerald-700">Sobre & Metodologia</a>
          <a href="/guia" class="hover:text-emerald-700">Guia de Compra</a>
          <a href="/como-usar" class="hover:text-emerald-700">Como Usar</a>
          <a href="/ferramentas/quiz-qual-ergometrica" class="hover:text-emerald-700">Quiz</a>
          <a href="/sitemap.xml" class="hover:text-emerald-700">Sitemap</a>
        </nav>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">
          © {new Date().getFullYear()} bicicletasergometricas.com · Participante dos programas de afiliados da Amazon, Shopee e Mercado Livre.
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
